d some tips on PVP please help is there a place I can read tips?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aanladil>Aanladil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/7/00 11:48:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Advice</span><hr size=1> You will not be able to afford this at your level unless you're a twink.  Go HEAVY magic resist.  If you're not at or above 75 MR, you're toast.<br>
<br>
Also, learn to circle strafe, and use fast weapons to interrupt the caster... most experienced casters will know to move around a lot to avoid the backstab, so don't focus too much on getting that backstab, although it is sweet when it happens.  More likely than not though you will either miss or get a measly 5 dmg backstab or something =P<br>
Try to stick to the caster like a leech, making sure he has no opportunity to channel through.<br>
<br>
Start learning poison, as it will help in later levels-- every little bit will help.<br>
<br>
And build up your throwing and/or archery.  If you're rooted, either apply poison or start poking him from afar to try to interrupt him.<br>
<br>
This is the stuff I've learned so far.  But I have never successfully killed a person-- just trying to stay alive so far. hehe.<br>
<br>
